## 📚 Documentation Standards

### README Requirements
- **Template**: Use `docs/templates/readme-template.md`
- **Must include**:
  - Emojis, badges, mermaid diagrams
  - Current infrastructure diagrams
  - Table of contents
  - Setup instructions and environment config
  - Troubleshooting guide
- **Update frequency**: With every repository change

### Terraform Variables
Structure `variables.tf` with clear section headers:
```hcl
#===================================#
#        < BASIC SETTINGS >         #
#===================================#

#===================================#
#        < NETWORK SETTINGS >       #
#===================================#

#===================================#
#        < TAGGING >                #
#===================================#
```

